WIRUlink has announced that it will offer specials of more than 50% off on selected wireless uncapped Internet packages this Black Friday. The deals will start on 23 November and will be available until the end of Cyber Monday (26 November). Customers can choose between a 10Mbps unshaped package for R659 per month, or a 15Mbps option for R799 per month. WIRUlink will only be offering 100 of these packages, and new customers will only start paying for their Internet in February 2019. “Black Friday and Cyber Monday are synonymous with consumer discounts and as a leading provider of wireless broadband Internet access in South Africa, we are excited to give consumers the opportunity to get connected,” said CTO Riaan Maree. You can learn more about these deals and pre-register on WIRUlink’s website.